<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC "-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Strict//EN" "http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-strict.dtd">
<html xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml"><head><title>flexbox | flex-wrap: wrap / long items</title>
<link href="http://opera.com" rel="author" title="Opera Software" />
<link href="http://www.w3.org/TR/css-flexbox-1/#propdef-flex-wrap" rel="help" />
<link href="reference/flexbox_wrap-long-ref.xht" rel="match" />
<style>
div {
	background: blue;
	margin: 1em 0;
	border: 1px solid black;
	width: 20em;

	display: flex;
	flex-wrap: wrap;
}
span {
	background: white;
	margin: 1em;
	width: 8em;
	display: inline-block;
}
span:first-child {
	width: 24em;
}
</style>

</head><body><div>
	<span>one</span>
	<span>two</span>
	<span>three</span>
	<span>four</span>
</div>
</body></html>